{"tid":677422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國總理親自探訪「中國維權律師」的妻子, 關注中國人權","createTime":"2018-05-25T07:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T00:54:16.000Z","uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c092060070fea200a2b8264510151d37f18049","tid":677422,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"中國民主唔關香港人事, 咁關德國人咩事?  正一死左膠  <br />\n<br />\nDonald Trump 都講過: 香港的反共抗爭跟美國無關, 美國政府不要多管閒事.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/2080489/?lcc=ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2080489%2F%3Flcc%3Dac&d=YbuBPTZzxgtB6n4KcdqCx4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=fb57f9a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/2080489/?lcc=ac</a><br />\n<br />\n默克爾訪華 會見維權律師余文生妻子<br />\n政治 14:02 2018/05/25 <br />\n <br />\n根據來自推特的訊息，正在中國訪問的德國總理默克爾，24日會見中國維權律師余文生的妻子許豔，兩人並合影留念。余文生於1月19日被捕入獄至今，罪名是「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」。<br />\n<br />\n中國維權人士姚建清今天清晨在她的推特帳號Yao Jianqing推文表示，默克爾在中國，接見了中國人權律師余文生的妻子許豔，雙方就中國的人權問題交換了意見，並附上一張默克爾與許豔的合照。<br />\n<br />\n推文沒有說明兩人昨天會面的時間地點以及進一步的談話內容，德國官方至截稿前也沒有發布相關消息。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾展示關切中國人權<br />\n<br />\n德國此前非常關切余文生。1月30日，德國人權專員柯夫勒（Barbel Kofler）呼籲中國當局立刻放人，並表示「余文生所做的一切都是為了中國民主改革，他支持那些因為行使人權而受到騷擾的同胞」。"},{"pid":"bd183503974fcb383be51198c42a83afa7eb3d41","tid":677422,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump: 香港的反共抗爭跟美國無關. 美國政府勿多管閒事.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/517097817702412288?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F517097817702412288%3Flang%3Den&d=YbuBPTZzxgtB6n4KcdqCx4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7a40ffcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F517097817702412288%3Flang%3Den&h=f12f07a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/517097817702412288?lang=en</a><br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump<br />\n&rlm;Verified account <br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n<br />\nPresident Obama should stay out of the Hong Kong protests, we have enough problems in our own country!Can't even properly police White House<br />\n<br />\n4:45 PM - 30 Sep 2014"},{"pid":"68597d5ed948abd2efccdec48a27c864888ad9b8","tid":677422,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd389238f8d9e6b2571e6cffc1561e2eb4c75fb6","tid":677422,"uid":55951,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"偽善者<br />\n呢頭慰問完，嗰頭就同雜種食飯嘅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50364a5903861ec8cf7eb00c2f32b00f110f7ed","tid":677422,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"口交部：強烈反對別國干涉中國內政"},{"pid":"e494080feb9d88a52b8c74bf9cffefa1d44bf2c0","tid":677422,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dd389238f8d9e6b2571e6cffc1561e2eb4c75fb6","tid":677422,"uid":55951,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"偽善者<br />\n呢頭慰問完，嗰頭就同雜種食飯嘅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"其他人連慰問都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n侵侵仲話雜種係永遠朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4ec1b881244115dcfe71eff4b2ef0263d2cacd","tid":677422,"uid":56302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd389238f8d9e6b2571e6cffc1561e2eb4c75fb6","tid":677422,"uid":55951,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"偽善者<br />\n呢頭慰問完，嗰頭就同雜種食飯嘅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-